         <p>Arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection consists of 24 programs of concerts held in New Haven from 1824 to 1859. Included are performances by such well-known musicians as the Hutchinson Family Singers, the soprano Jenny Lind, and the violinist Ole Bull.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
